The Lighting:

Soft, flat, overhead studio lighting (shadowless).

Output:

 A single 4:5 image.

The Year (e.g., "1955") should be arranged using physical typography (like metal letters or cut paper) placed in the center of the grid. 

Style: Wes Anderson symmetry, high-end commercial advertising, vibrant.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G8kHpzdXkAAhBsv.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2002307108050776474", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-20T09:16:30.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Gadgetify\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Gdgtify\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
