VALUES ('Brand Concept Generation Prompt: Unexpected Functional Objects', 'A sophisticated prompt template for Nano Banana Pro that automatically generates high-end, conceptual magazine photography of a unique, unexpected functional object designed through the lens of a specified brand''s philosophy and materials.', '{argument name="品牌名称" default="[品牌名称]"}：  
