VALUES ('Molten Voxel Transformation Prompt', 'A prompt for Nano Banana Pro designed to transform an uploaded subject photo into a ''Molten Voxel'' state. It mandates preserving the exact pose and geometry while rendering the subject as cooling volcanic rock with internal magma veins, using pyro-solver simulation and high-contrast, emissive lighting.', 'Input A is the subject photo. Preserve exact pose and scene geometry.
