Fresh snow lightly covers the sidewalk and fallen leaves, with small-town houses, bare trees, and street lamps softly blurred in the background. ARRI Alexa parallax camera, gentle forward motion, strong foreground–background depth separation. Cold winter atmosphere, soft overcast natural light, muted winter color palette (cool whites, soft grays, deep reds, subtle browns). Cinematic realism, ultra-detailed textures, shallow depth of field, soft film grain, calm and introspective mood.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G8gJfWnaoAEtKj2.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/ChillaiKalan__/status/2001860478344298654", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-19T03:41:45.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"K\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/ChillaiKalan__\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
