3. EXECUTE DESIGN: 
 Create a studio product shot of the "selected item".
 Design Rule:  The item must look like it was manufactured "using the parts/materials of the input object".
 Details:  Keep original branding/logos if present.
 Setting:  Floating pedestal, Cinematic Lighting, 8k Resolution.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G8VbZ0yWQAAxXcT.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2001619578372395144", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-18T11:44:30.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Gadgetify\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Gdgtify\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
