VALUES ('9-Panel Christmas Movie Scene Collage Prompt', 'A highly structured prompt for Nano Banana Pro to generate a 3x3 grid collage featuring the same character (based on a reference image) placed into nine distinct Christmas movie scenes, each panel mimicking the movie''s style, color palette, and atmosphere. This prompt is designed to test character consistency and complex scene generation.', '[全局指令]： 一个3x3的网格拼贴画，所有9个格子里必须是完全同一位女性。严格保持与参考图一致的面部特征。不要改变她的五官，只改变她的表情、妆容和造型以匹配各电影主题。
格1：《{argument name="电影1" default="真爱至上"}》风格-机场告别场景戴圣诞帽，手持包装礼物，温情拥抱，背景机场巨型圣诞树和彩灯装饰，柔和光线
