ified delicate water-ink illustration style. make the aspect ratio 16:9.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/DanAdvantage/status/2000333914192113673", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-14T22:35:44.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Dan Advantage\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/DanAdvantage\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
