VALUES ('Cinematic Behind-the-Scenes VFX Artists Prompt', 'A photorealistic, cinematic prompt for generating a behind-the-scenes shot of two male special effects artists being interviewed, featuring professional film equipment, a workbench covered in disassembled animatronic parts of a fantasy creature, and technical schematics on an easel.', 'A photorealistic, cinematic behind-the-scenes shot of two male special effects artists sitting in canvas director chairs giving an interview. They are gesturing enthusiastically. In the foreground, professional film cameras and a boom mic are visible, framing the shot. Next to the men is a workbench covered in the disassembled animatronic parts of a fantasy creature (a fluffy white beast with teal icy scales and large blue eyes), showing internal servos, cabling, and the detached head. Behind them is a large presentation easel displaying complex, hand-drawn technical schematics and engineering notes in black marker. Studio lighting, sharp focus, 8k resolution, documentary style.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G791QQmWMAEn7sM.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G791SBmWoAAhOUO.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/david_dark0/status/1999446520379109449", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-12T11:49:33.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"David Darko\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/david_dark0\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
