INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Vintage Action Figure Toyification Prompt', 'A complex, multi-phase prompt designed to transform an input subject into a vintage action figure, complete with plastic texture, articulation joints, custom accessories, and packaging design elements like a worn cardback and retro typography, resulting in a photorealistic macro shot of the toy mint-on-card.', '<instruction>
**Phase 1: Toyification**
1. **Plasticity:** Convert the subject''s skin and clothing into semi-gloss ABS plastic textures. Visible joints at elbows and knees.
2. **Accessory** Analyze the subject''s profession or hobby (or infer it). Generate 2 distinct "accessories" included in the bubble (e.g., a tiny plastic laptop, a sword, a coffee mug).
3. **Era:** Determine if the vibe is 80s (Neon/He-Man), 90s (Grungy/Spawn), or 70s (Kenner/Star Wars).

**Phase 2: Packaging Design**
1. **Cardback Art:** The cardboard backing features a dynamic 2D illustration of the subject in an action pose behind the plastic bubble.
2. **Wear & Tear:** The card corners must be slightly frayed/white. The plastic bubble should have minor scratches or yellowing to simulate age.
3. **Typography:** Bold, explosive comic book fonts. Title: "the [Subject''s Defining Trait]".

**Phase 3: The Shot**
A slightly high-angle studio shot of the unpromoted toy resting on a wooden table or carpet, as if just found at a garage sale.
</instruction>

A photorealistic macro shot of a vintage action figure mint-on-card. The figure inside the yellowed plastic blister pack is the input subject turned into a plastic toy with visible articulation joints. The cardboard backing features retro character art. Worn edges, price tag sticker residue. 1990s toy aesthetic.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G77NwVoXcAA-I3x.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G77Nw_bWkAADfKX.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/1999602411619442822", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-12T22:09:00.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Gadgetify\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Gdgtify\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
