INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Alluring Christmas Scene with Firelight', 'An extremely detailed Nano Banana Pro prompt for generating an intimate, hyper-realistic Christmas scene. It features a young woman curled up in an armchair beside a roaring fireplace, wearing a festive velvet dress. The prompt specifies technical camera settings (85mm f/1.8, wide aperture, specific shutter speed/ISO) to create a shallow depth of field, creamy bokeh from Christmas lights, and warm, flickering firelight painting the subject''s skin and dress.', 'A cozy-yet-alluring Christmas scene, reimagined. A stunning young woman with golden blonde, beachy waves is curled up in a large, plush armchair directly beside a crackling fireplace. She wears a short, festive dress—think a deep {argument name="dress color" default="emerald green or burgundy"} velvet with a delicate lace trim, featuring a slightly loose, off-shoulder neckline that reveals her collarbones and a hem that ends mid-thigh. Her bare legs are curled beneath her, one knee drawn up, showcasing her toned legs as a central focal point.

The room is a cozy Christmas haven: the mantle glows with candles and pine garlands, a beautifully lit tree twinkles softly in the background (rendered in creamy bokeh), and a half-finished mug of hot chocolate sits on a side table. The primary, mesmerizing light is the warm, flickering glow from the roaring fire, painting golden-orange highlights on her skin, the velvet of her dress, and the smooth curves of her legs.

Her pose is intimate and captivating. She leans slightly forward, resting her chin in her hand, her elbow propped on the chair''s arm. Her expression is a soft, knowing smile directed at the camera, eyes sparkling with reflected firelight. One hand rests casually on her raised knee, drawing subtle attention to her legs. The pose is relaxed, natural, and effortlessly sensual.

Technical execution: Shot from a low angle (slightly below her eye level) and close-medium distance to emphasize the length of her legs and the cozy setting. An 85mm f/1.8 lens compresses the scene beautifully, creating a shallow depth of field that melts the Christmas lights into soft, glowing spheres while keeping her face, décolletage, and legs tack-sharp. Aperture is wide open (f/1.8). A shutter speed of 1/60s captures the dynamic flicker of the flames. ISO 2500 adds a fine, cinematic grain. Color grading is rich and festive: deep emeralds/reds, warm amber firelight, and cool shadows. The aesthetic is hyper-realistic, intimate, and beautifully festive—a private holiday moment of warm allure.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7574RLWgAEi8d1.png"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/logicpromt/status/1999171543633477906", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-11T17:36:53.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Alexa\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/logicpromt\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
