VALUES ('Aerial Beach Selfie with Cheeky Wink', 'A highly technical prompt simulating an aerial ''Shot on iPhone'' aesthetic, captured by a drone over water. The subject is a young woman with freckles, wearing a black polka dot bikini, winking and sticking her tongue out. The prompt specifies detailed facial features, attire, and uses technical mobile photography terms (Deep Fusion, Smart HDR) for ultra-fine detail and dynamic range.', 'Subject:
