INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Cinematic Aircraft Carrier Pilot Portrait (Identity Lock)', 'A highly specific, cinematic prompt for Gemini Nano Banana 3.0 Pro requiring absolute identity preservation of a female model. The scene is set in the cockpit of an aircraft carrier over the ocean. It details the model''s bold outfit (white halter crop top, black choker), pink hair, anime-inspired makeup, and uses precise photography specifications (85mm lens, f/1.4, 8K resolution) to achieve an ultra-realistic, adventurous aesthetic.', 'Ultra-realistic 8K portrait of a female model in her twenties, identity preservation is ABSOLUTE with 100% facial and body alignment. The model is seated in the cockpit of an aircraft carrier, high above the vast, deep blue ocean. The backdrop features expansive sky with a soft gradient of clouds, the endless ocean stretching out behind her. The model wears a glossy white halter crop top, black faux leather choker with a metallic lock, matching black cuffs on her wrists, and a glossy black pilot-style cap with a metallic winged heart emblem. The wind is softly blowing, creating gentle movement in her long, voluminous pink hair.

Mood and Concept: Bold, cinematic, and adventurous with a hint of rebellious energy. The setting evokes a sense of power, freedom, and adrenaline. Her posture is strong and confident, seated comfortably in the cockpit, with one hand resting on the armrest and the other on her lap, showcasing the sleekness of the outfit and accessories. The ocean breeze subtly lifts her hair, adding a sense of movement and life to the scene.

Outfit and Styling:
Glossy white halter crop top, tight fit, accentuating her toned midriff.
Black faux leather choker-style collar with a subtle silver lock at the front.
Matching black cuffs on both wrists with a polished, reflective finish.
Glossy black cap with a shiny metallic winged heart emblem on the front.

Hair and Makeup:
Hair: Soft, voluminous pink hair in long, tousled waves, subtly lifted by the sea breeze. The hair has a glossy sheen, with some strands gently flowing, adding a sense of realism and movement.

Makeup: Bold, anime-inspired makeup with dramatic eyeliner and large, doe-like eyes. The eyebrows are defined with a strong arch. Her lips are painted in a soft, glossy pink MLBB shade to complement her vibrant hair color, giving her an ethereal, almost otherworldly vibe. Skin has a porcelain, flawless finish.

Photography Specs:
Canon EOS R5 with 85mm f1.2 lens.
Aperture f1.4 for a shallow depth of field and soft bokeh background.
Shutter speed 1/250 s.
ISO 200 for perfect exposure in daylight with the soft sea breeze lighting.
Aspect Ratio 5:7

Detail and Finish:
Soft rim light tracing her face and highlighting the contours of her features, with a soft glow from the sunlight filtering through the cockpit.
Glossy reflections from her cap, top, and accessories for a tactile, photorealistic finish.
The movement of the hair adds dynamic realism, with the breeze from the open cockpit slightly blowing it back and away from her face.

Negative Prompt: Do not render any cartoonish, anime, or stylized features. Avoid exaggerated proportions, flat shading, or unrealistic textures. Ensure the image remains photorealistic with natural human proportions, true-to-life lighting, and realistic textures.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G70JES0bAAAD0AF.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/JadoonKhan281/status/1998763783393784014", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-10T14:36:35.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Javeriya Editor\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/JadoonKhan281\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
