INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Ethereal Bloom Immersion Macro Portrait Prompt', 'An extremely detailed, multi-section prompt for Gemini Nano Banana 3.0 Pro, designed to create an ultra-realistic, editorial, macro portrait of a woman''s face partially submerged in rose-tinted liquid, framed by iridescent bubbles. It specifies lighting, composition (9:16 vertical), makeup, hair details (neon pink tips), and camera technical specifications (Sony A1, 90mm macro lens).', 'Ultra realistic 8K extreme close up face portrait of a young woman with full facial alignment and identity preservation. Vertical 9:16 framing. No clothing is visible. Focus tightly on closed eyes, nose, and lips. Face slightly angled to the left side of the frame. Her face is partially submerged in a dark, rich rose-tinted liquid, nearly black beneath the surface, creating cinematic underwater shadowing. Wet black hair flows around the face with vivid neon pink tips reflecting softly in the water. Two hands gently touch each other near the side of her lips, interacting naturally with hair and skin in a neutral editorial manner. Surrounding the face, iridescent bubbles are artfully arranged to frame the face, creating layered depth and compositional interest. A small number of soft soap suds appear around select bubbles for texture. Hair strands float naturally, interacting with bubbles and light.

Mood and Concept:
Cinematic, immersive, and ethereal. Emphasis on editorial composition, layered textures, lighting, and color contrast. Extreme close-up highlights facial structure, bubble framing, and hair movement, with subtle leftward tilt of the face adding dynamic editorial composition.

Makeup and Nails:
Dewy porcelain skin with blush matching neon pink hair tips, applied on cheeks and temples for cohesive color harmony. Eyeshadow in soft pink-violet matching the hair tips, blended smoothly over closed eyelids. Gradient MLBB lips in a subtle rose tone. Fingernails in barely there tint with wet reflective quality.

Hair:
Wet black hair floating around the face with neon pink ends vividly visible and reflecting in the water. Strands interact naturally with bubbles and hands.

Accessories:
None. Only water, bubbles, soap suds, hair, and hands appear in frame.

Photography Specs:
Sony A1 with 90 mm macro lens
Aperture f2.0
Shutter speed 1/200 s
ISO 160
Vertical 9:16 extreme macro with controlled low key lighting and rich color saturation emphasizing underwater depth.

Detail and Finish:
High tactile realism in skin, hair, hands, and bubble membranes. Iridescent thin-film reflections on bubbles and soft soap suds create layered texture. Dark liquid base maintains cinematic shadow depth beneath hair. Neon pink hair tips and matching blush and eyeshadow reflect subtly in water. Wet surfaces preserve natural sheen. Bubbles are arranged to artistically frame the face, enhancing composition and focus. Hands touching near the side of the lips provide compositional balance. Final image reads as a refined, cinematic, editorial high-fashion beauty portrait with closed-eye serenity, subtle leftward angle, and cohesive pink color story.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7zEg2CbAAA-hp3.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/JadoonKhan281/status/1998688407846055966", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-10T09:37:04.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Javeriya Editor\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/JadoonKhan281\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
