INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Golden Hour Noir Car Selfie with Flash', 'A highly detailed prompt for a high-contrast, glamorous car selfie taken at night with a hard, direct on-camera flash. It specifies the subject''s appearance (blonde hair, glass-skin, glossy lips, 90s sunglasses), attire (sequin tube top), accessories (gold jewelry), and technical details (24mm lens, f/2.8, cinematic color grading, hyper-realistic style).', 'Golden hour-turned-noir car selfie. A young woman with sun-streaked blonde hair—textured, layered, with effortless bedhead volume—casts a seductive, knowing look over the rim of her 90s rectangle rimless sunglasses (brown gradient lenses, gold bridge). Her skin is porcelain-white with a hyper-glowy, glass-skin finish; intense specular highlights blaze on her cheekbones and the tip of her nose. Her hazel-green eyes squint slightly. Plump, glossy nude-pink lips are slightly parted, with the subtle, playful press of her tongue against her teeth.

She wears a high-reflectivity champagne-silver sequin tube top, each sequin catching the light as a distinct point of glitter. Her right hand, adorned with stacked chunky gold dome rings on multiple fingers, adjusts the sunglasses frame on her nose. Her left hand is splayed against her chest, showcasing Cartier-style gold love bangles on her wrist.

The scene is inside a luxury car''s dark leather interior at night. Through the rear window, out-of-focus city lights melt into a creamy, dark bokeh. The mood is intimate and moody, shattered by the stark, high-contrast blast of a hard, direct on-camera flash. The flash freezes every detail: the texture in her hair, the sparkle of sequins, the gleam of jewelry, and the dewy skin, creating deep, inky shadows.

Shot with a feel akin to a Canon G7X Mark II or iPhone 15 Pro Night Mode with flash—using a wide 24mm lens for a slight, intimate distortion. Aperture at f/2.8 for sharp focus on the face and jewelry against the blurred lights. Color grading is warm and cinematic: saturated golden skin tones, rich blacks, and a touch of filmic grain. The aesthetic is hyper-realistic, sharp, and effortlessly cool—a candid moment loaded with glamour.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G7zPdx5XMAAM8Jl.png"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/logicpromt/status/1998700503136342090", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-10T10:25:08.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Alexa\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/logicpromt\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
